content.productFullDescription:
The Pearl Izumi Attack bike jersey is packed with features to give you everything you need for a comfortable cool-weather ride without breaking the bank.

  • Moisture-transfer fabric moves sweat to outer surface for quick evaporation
  • Fabric provides UPF 50+ sun protection, shielding skin from harmful ultraviolet rays
  • Full-length zipper allows fventing; elasticized gripper on back keeps hem in place
  • 3 rear pockets expand to store cycling essentials and food
  • The Pearl Izumi Attack bike jersey has reflective accents to keep you visible in low-light
  • Semifitted design enhances performance and prevents fabric from flapping in slipstream
